5.title: About the Conference
5.text: Meet the people who are leading the economic sector and learn the way you should do it such that everything gets to be perfect. You will find yourself between equally talented individuals, their stories, ideas, struggle and passion.

6.title: How to Attend
6.text: Learn about the benefits, opportunities and exposure that come from exhibiting your business in Startup Alley — from founders just like you. Now, 2020 is a year like no other — not exactly a newsflash, right? Digital Startup Alley may be virtual, but the connections and opportunities that come from exhibiting there are very real.
